ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A good background on complex math. A rollercoaster but a fun one. Does a good job introducing many different aspects of modern math. Definitely recommend for someone looking to expand their knowledge of math.
I would definitely recommend this course to another student as the one can really enjoy the beauty of math during this course.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I enjoyed getting some good math in, though it wasn't directly related to my research. I do feel like I have a better foundation for math related topics doing my analyses of data.
I did study measure theory before but this course helped me to see the whole picture.
